Installation
------------

### Linux

1. Download the latest release from the [Releases page](https://github.com/compiledkernel-idk/FlashDL/releases).
2. Extract the archive:
   ```bash
   tar -xzvf FlashDL-linux.tar.gz
   ```
3. Run the binary:
   ```bash
   ./FlashDL-linux/flashdl [URL]
   ```

### Windows

Currently, you must build from source using MinGW-w64.
1. Install MinGW-w64.
2. Run `./mingw-config`.
3. Run `make`.

